(67384, 7063, 6127, 1, 'When I''m with You (Westpoint) ', '　Westpoint是由5位傑出音樂人組合而成，Westpoint與多倫多重量級的製作人Joel Kazmi在2007年共同完成首張專輯【Goodbye Rocket】。並於同年獲得「多倫多獨立音樂獎」的《最佳搖滾獎》與《另類樂團獎》。 \r\n　2008年在加拿大展開一些巡演宣傳【Goodbye Rocket】專輯。Westpoint令人振奮的音樂、熱情的嗓音和有感染力的創作，肯定在聽過一次後，就會跟著唱。\r\n', '2013-10-21 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 15, '『When I''m With You』\r\n\r\nWhen you come inside of my head\r\nwhen you  come I feel so glad\r\nYou turn me on then I''m on again\r\nyou fill me up then I''m home again\r\nwhen I''m with you~\r\n\r\nWhen you come I feel so glad\r\nwhen you go I feel so sad\r\nYou turn me on then I''m on again\r\nyou fill me up then I''m home again\r\nwhen I''m with you~\r\nyou take me high~\r\n\r\nYou turn me on then I''m on again\r\nyou fill me up then I''m home again\r\nwhen I''m with you~\r\n', '', 206, '', 'Mordechai Harroch + Stephen Andrews + Jeffrey William Kenny + Brandon Robinson + Daniel Raymond Walk', 'Mordechai Harroch + Stephen Andrews + Jeffrey William Kenny + Brandon Robinson + Daniel Raymond Walk', '', '藝見傳播', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-10-22 12:06:17', '2015-03-12 14:02:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
